Posting content with an 'include' macro in the storage format to the Confluence content convert API endpoint (/rest/api/contentbody/convert/<FORMAT>) returns an error that the included page could not be found.

The content that is posted comes directly from the macro body API endpoint (/rest/api/content/<PAGE_ID>/history/<PAGE_VERSION>/macro/id/<MACRO_ID>). Is this a bug or am I doing something wrong?

